      We use a multi-step verification process including mobile OTP verification and optional government ID verification. All profiles undergo review to maintain authenticity and trust on the platform.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <span>Is the dating platform free to use?</span>
      <button class="faq-toggle">+</button>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-answer">
      DatingMet offers 11 days of free access to explore profiles and features. After the trial period, you can choose from our affordable subscription plans to continue chatting and connecting.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <span>How to find a match quickly on DatingMet?</span>
      <button class="faq-toggle">+</button>
    </div>
